1. Open word doc, Alt+F8 Open macro, F5 Run. Key word AutoOpen runs on opening doc. 

Sub AutoOpen()
'
Dim xHttp
Set xHttp = CreateObject("Microsoft.XMLHTTP")
xHttp.Open "GET", "http://1.1.1.1/Does-not-exist.txt", False
xHttp.Send
' AutoOpen
End Sub

You may want to auto-exec. File > Options > Cust Ribbon > Enable Developer
